    "body": "Hi there. This looks like one weird issue. As /u/javaing pointed out, those steps should work. \n\nBased on the error message received, my guess is it has something to do with `npm`; it's likely that some SSL certificate got mangled along the way while it attempted to download the right packages. (Note: Truffle has no control over how `npm` structures their service).\n\nThis doesn't seem to be a Truffle error, so I'm going to close it for housekeeping issues. However, if you figure out the issue, please document it here as it might be of help to others. Thanks!",
